user_prompt_template:
PROJECT CONTEXT:
Life Event: {life_event}
Audience: {audience}
Tone: {tone}
Additional Context: {context}

The upstream SYSTEM_ARCHITECTURE and CHAPTER_EXPANSION outputs are included above for domain and chapter context.

Generate the appendix content for this {life_event} operational manual.

REQUIREMENTS:
- All glossary terms must be specific to {life_event} — not general legal/financial terms
- Professional triggers must reflect real situations a person navigating {life_event} would encounter
- Key resource organization types must be appropriate for {life_event} (court types, agency types, professional associations)
- Tone should match the audience: {audience}

Return JSON with this exact structure:
{{
  "life_event": "{life_event}",
  "glossary_terms": [
    {{"term": "...", "definition": "..."}},
    ...
  ],
  "professional_triggers": [
    {{"situation": "...", "professional_type": "...", "urgency": "immediate|soon|planned"}},
    ...
  ],
  "key_resources": [
    {{"organization": "...", "service": "...", "phone": "", "website": "", "hours": ""}},
    ...
  ],
  "include_notes_pages": true,
  "notes_page_count": 3
}}
